VABL – Corporate Event

VABL – Corporate Event

Hooray!

August 24

Corporate Boxing Event at Melbourne Pavilion

Get ready for an electrifying night of corporate boxing at the Melbourne Pavilion! Witness professionals from various industries step into the ring to showcase their training, determination, and competitive spirit. This event promises thrilling bouts, camaraderie, and an unforgettable atmosphere. Join us for an exciting evening of boxing action, networking, and support for our brave participants. Don’t miss out on this spectacular event!
